verse.name: v1
verse.lines: He is exalted, the King is exalted on high, I will praise Him. He is exalted, for ever exalted And I will praise his name.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines: He is the Lord, for ever His truth shall reign. Heaven and earth rejoice in His holy name. He is exalted, the King is exalted on high.
